data.description: Largo pool home w/ 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, guest suite with seperate full kitchen w/ appliances and full bath. Fenced rear yard with covered porch, caged pool, new shed with loft, 6 zone irrigation and attached carport. Other features include oak kitchen w/ granite countertops, fridge only 3 months new, lots of custom lighting, tankless water heater, HVAC 6 years, split unit in guest suite.
